{"tid":1633374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:51:30.000Z","uid":281029,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5099737a144b4f10123bd971d8e4c5ee9a687a9","tid":1633374,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【文宣核彈】搞左呢份野等三萬黑警都要接受國際審判<br />\n<br />\n[繼續Post] 話說我地花左兩個月時間, 睇左過百條片, 終於<br />\n我地製作左文宣核彈, 係 270 頁黑警濫權獨立調查報告<br />\n<br />\n但係咁岩撞正連登熄登,<br />\n無咩人推, 幾日過千正評都無<br />\n我好灰, 但我唔會放棄<br />\n唯有硬著頭皮, 開新 Post 推多次<br />\n同法律港女一樣, 我地會做實事,<br />\n依家搞緊英文翻譯, 然後就會製作文宣, 推向國際, 推向全世界<br />\n到時係聯合國好, 海牙好, 紐倫堡好, 美國國會, 英國國會, 歐盟<br />\n全部都係我地射程範圍<br />\n但係真係要大家廣傳, 所以希望大家真係唔好俾呢個POST 沉<br />\n好多人睇到唔訓覺, 工都辭埋, 甚至要抑鬱睇精神科<br />\n大家都係想香港贏, 香港人贏, 所以唔該唔好等我地心血白費<br />\n<br />\n中文版本&mdash;公眾試閱版&mdash;正文<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k%2Fedit&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4hR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=cef46223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1N1rzVWFW0EnJugLGNkYu7A-9-KigPWn4fVEGVDve79k/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（六／七月）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI%2Fedit&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4hR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=91b5cdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1RMY12ApIxNTaOudzjvYXzq6Vc0iE99zJJ2M8t0uOKYI/edit</a><br />\n警隊涉嫌濫權資料（至八月十日）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89-VTMIsfNAiFsuXX4g1r8/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1TKPNvv_YqRKF8Y2wRi28J89